Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.54,0:00:17.77,Main,fish,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.17,0:00:26.25,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,S-See you later?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.67,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.33,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.02,0:00:36.26,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,This fish has scales \NI've never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.33,Flashback,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Fish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.21,0:00:43.85,Flashback,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:00:58.94,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,This sake is rather weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.94,0:01:01.40,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Must be dog piss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.69,0:01:07.06,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.06,0:01:09.21,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,My side dish to go with my sake is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:13.53,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.92,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:18.11,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.47,0:01:22.15,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, and that, \Nand that, and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.72,0:01:28.35,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't the taste of\N Mukaido's granny's cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.35,0:01:30.66,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.66,0:01:32.28,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:34.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I did something rather rude to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.58,0:01:37.49,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and wasted some food on top of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.39,0:01:43.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... going to curse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.05,Episode-Title - Copy,title,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2: The Chilly Desert
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:26.10,Main,bg,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:29.43,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:34.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.17,Main,tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.17,0:03:37.69,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, I couldn't be better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.19,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:40.47,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:45.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.63,0:03:47.15,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.03,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:54.72,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for taking care \Nof Manaka yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.88,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.28,0:03:58.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:01.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Surface people have no business concerning \Nthemselves with the Village of the Sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:06.39,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:08.83,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:13.60,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun! That was really rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:14.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:17.91,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about it! You had a rough \Ntime because of him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:19.53,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:21.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's because of the surface people!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's guilty by association!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:26.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... Tsumugu-kun saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.61,0:04:30.58,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"Tsu-mu-gu-kun"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-Why are you so mad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:35.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're suddenly sounding \Nso buddy-buddy with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.33,0:04:36.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.84,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then Tsumugu... san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I don't know his last name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.94,0:04:46.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting really \Nstrange lately, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.91,0:04:48.64,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And you're always so angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:50.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.65,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:07.46,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:11.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I-I messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.12,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Messed up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:16.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun saved me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.52,0:05:21.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But Hii-kun worried \Nabout me a lot, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,and I yelled at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.58,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.58,0:05:26.26,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:29.99,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari was really worried \Nabout you, Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.14,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.04,0:05:33.28,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:37.31,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Even though his Ena was dry, and \Nhe couldn't breathe that well,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.56,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,he was really determined...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.08,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:42.53,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari isn't really mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.95,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So try not to be afraid of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.95,0:05:47.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That'll just annoy him even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:50.35,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.71,0:05:54.13,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know all this, Chii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,About Hii-kun's feelings and my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:02.17,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It's because I've been watching \Nyou guys since we were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.17,0:06:03.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Both you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:05.79,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.41,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop, Forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:14.35,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're the two from the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:18.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:20.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"That woman"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:21.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:22.81,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.06,0:06:24.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She's my older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.86,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! You octopus-head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"O-Octopus"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:30.77,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,He was calling her by her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.58,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,They've got to be a couple, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.98,0:06:36.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I don't really know \Nwhat's going on here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.87,0:06:39.45,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,but shouldn't you two be in school?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.18,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Your teacher's going to get mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:43.59,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't treat me like a brat, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need some brat telling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.61,0:06:50.79,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.50,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You brought backup, you cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:55.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, you're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:57.10,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:58.98,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't pick on little kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.02,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.95,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't touch me with \Nyour fishy-smelly hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.03,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.28,0:07:10.11,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.11,0:07:10.68,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.76,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Serves you rice dumplings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:15.95,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:23.84,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right, that's the end of class for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.22,0:07:25.71,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:29.06,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Who here wants to try \Nto make an Ojoushi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.28,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,What's an "Ojoushi-sama"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.93,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean the doll we'd \Nsend off in the Ofunehiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.93,0:07:34.80,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.29,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Originally, when the Ofunehiki started,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.29,0:07:42.94,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,a girl would be sent off as a \Nsacrifice and offered to the Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.94,0:07:45.46,Main,each,0000,0000,0000,,Nowadays, instead of an actual girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:48.44,Main,each,0000,0000,0000,,we send off a wooden doll \Ncalled an Ojoushi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.93,0:07:51.15,Main,girl,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to make an Ojoushi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:53.41,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't adults supposed \Nto do that kind of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:56.58,Main,girl b,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I heard they weren't doing \Nthe Ofunehiki this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:58.97,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:01.23,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,that's why we were \Nthinking of doing
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:04.91,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,something like a voluntary \NOfunehiki at our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.91,0:08:06.83,Main,kids,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.83,0:08:07.79,Main,boy C,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:08.76,Main,boy d,0000,0000,0000,,So annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.76,0:08:10.76,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:11.42,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone who wants to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.21,0:08:19.93,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:36.66,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why do we have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.24,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,This is the job of the surface people!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:42.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't have volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.68,0:08:46.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The surface people don't have a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:48.22,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we have to \Nkeep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.25,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.08,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you offer to make this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.91,Main,tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,My family are fishermen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.35,0:08:57.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,We live off the sea, so I wanted the\Nchance to give the proper thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:59.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That means we need to do the Ofunehiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.74,0:09:03.37,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that Uroko-sama actually exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.37,0:09:04.77,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.23,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,He's sort of a pervy old man though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.15,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,He's sort of in between an \Nold man and a young guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.81,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So he does exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.24,0:09:14.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about saltflake snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.92,0:09:17.22,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,When salt falls down like snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.22,0:09:20.84,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and if sacred fire \Nburns inside the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.49,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,then how do you actually \Nget it to go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:27.12,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You know quite a bit, Tsumugu-kun,\Nabout Shioshishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.29,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:32.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,On days that are really sunny,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.76,0:09:34.41,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,because of the refraction of the light,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.66,0:09:37.33,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,there are times when you can \Njust make out the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.74,0:09:42.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,White roofs reflect \Nlight among the swells...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.78,0:09:45.36,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just like the sound of waves,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:50.50,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear singing resound\N farther, then nearer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:55.19,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I think the Village of the Sea is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:10:00.53,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,For someone on the surface to \Ncare so much about the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.49,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:19.19,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's about time you \Nsea kiddos headed home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:20.60,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.05,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:28.31,Main,girls,0000,0000,0000,,Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.44,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.94,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful heading home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:34.19,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.16,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:45.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei called us "sea kiddos."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:48.10,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That was actually kind of cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:52.96,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I sort of get that he's not a bad guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.70,0:10:54.64,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.83,0:11:00.66,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that Akari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.34,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.50,0:11:19.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,K-K-K-Ki...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:20.86,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,No, Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:35.57,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if that's her boyfriend...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:39.27,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She never even mentioned having a guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.27,0:11:42.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention a guy from the surface?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.12,0:11:44.59,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Akari-san is reaching the age when \Nshe's old enough to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.32,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she plans \Non leaving the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:48.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way it'd work out \Nwith a guy from the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:53.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they got married, she'd \Nend up coming right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.03,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.81,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Not possible? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:11:58.84,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.84,0:12:01.95,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,Because Akari-san looks like \Nshe'd make a great mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:03.74,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,She wouldn't end up coming right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.00,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.46,0:12:08.69,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If you end up with someone \Nfrom the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:11.04,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be banished from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.40,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,"Banished"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.40,0:12:21.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell—that's\N an awful thing to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.30,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What are you yelling at me for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:27.05,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that rule's \Nbeen around for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:28.56,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I've never heard of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.56,0:12:31.35,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,But Satsuki-san from the candy store,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:33.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and Koji-niisan from \Nthe Hara-san's family
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:36.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,went up to the surface and \Nnever came back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.21,0:12:37.23,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought that the \Npeople who didn't come back
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.09,0:12:42.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,just didn't come back because \Nthey threw away the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:45.78,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:50.51,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong with wanting to become \Nfamily with the person that's precious to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:52.10,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wonderful thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.83,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And for them to be chased \Nout of the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:59.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean... you think you want \N to get with a guy from the surface, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:00.69,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.04,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I hate it when you say \Nperverted things, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.04,0:13:06.01,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And I hate it when you say \Nperverted things, too, Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.81,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't said anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.81,0:13:08.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You did too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.51,0:13:10.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're really grossing me out lately!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.56,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, but\Nthat was so mean to Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.56,0:13:21.80,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean you "understand"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.80,0:13:22.53,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:25.41,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with you, always \Nacting like you're the adult?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.21,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You act like you know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:29.12,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you know about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:37.48,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That really wasn't right.\NYou just took it all out on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.38,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.77,0:13:42.60,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I understand why you'd get \Nirritated with Manaka, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:43.96,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.30,0:13:47.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is with those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.32,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Repeating that they understand \Nlike a broken record.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:53.28,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:56.74,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,don't really understand \Nexactly how I'm feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:18.47,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,The saltflake snow is pretty intense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.77,0:14:22.13,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And since no one cleans it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.91,0:14:25.53,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,It would have been nice to be \Nable to stay at Nami Junior High.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.67,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So you think things like that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That you want to stay here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:37.77,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't like \Nthe people on the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but I want to stay in the sea forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:44.60,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,With Manaka, you... and Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:51.41,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You want to stay here just \Nbecause that's easier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:57.37,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If you start longing for other \Nplaces, it'll become difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:57.41,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If you start longing for other \Nplaces, it'll become difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:02.08,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.71,0:15:07.71,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that Manaka was the first one \Nto take the first step out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.09,0:15:12.10,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Akiyoshi, Ukita, Kamon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:14.83,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.87,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara-kun, Kihara-kun, Kihara-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.71,0:15:23.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Now Hii-kun won't get angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.13,0:15:26.42,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.99,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If they got your DNA, \Nit sucks to be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:33.66,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You idiot! You saw the \Nfootage! It was super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.03,0:15:38.35,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Akari...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:41.39,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Today, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.39,0:15:43.74,Italics,Tv BG,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And this is our baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.74,0:15:44.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:47.65,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Oh, how cute. Does she \Nlook more like you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:47.19,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, it's a girl... I'm envious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.76,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,When I have a kid, I want \Nit to be a girl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:51.79,Italics,tg bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Well, she might have her father's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.47,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.47,0:15:53.35,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a younger sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:55.73,Italics,tg bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Lately, she started mimicking \Nme. Did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:55.73,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I was totally bummed when you came out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:57.93,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I didn't, but what does she do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:57.15,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.15,0:15:58.77,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I really am envious...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.93,0:16:02.90,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}If I say "me," she'll say "me" back, \Nand if I say "mo," she'll say "mo."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.90,0:16:04.35,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}But if I say "memo"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.43,Flashback,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If you end up with someone \Nfrom the surface,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.80,0:16:09.86,Flashback,kana,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be banished from the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:12.22,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Your baby will continue to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.22,0:16:14.75,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's a lot of work, but \Nevery day is a lot of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.41,Italics,tv bg,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Spoken like a true mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.35,0:16:24.65,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the \Ngirl from Shioshishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.92,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.25,0:16:30.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.43,0:16:32.88,Main,gramps,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.67,0:16:59.12,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,A guy from the surface, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:09.25,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I just... wanted to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:14.29,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect her like Ena does.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.26,0:17:19.49,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to protect her from \Neverything that could hurt her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:20.85,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:33.19,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to cast off all of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:36.19,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Cast off everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.10,0:17:39.79,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,And go to the world outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:58.09,Main,chisaki,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how big the kimono should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:17:59.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.86,0:18:00.43,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumu—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:02.89,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Kihara-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.65,0:18:05.71,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.02,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:10.17,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,We were wondering how wide the \NOjoushi-sama is around the waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.22,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,One sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.58,0:18:17.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why it still sounds pervy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,even when I use his last name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.64,0:18:23.57,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... It's n-nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:25.37,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,How's he doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:31.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,He... seems to be sleeping today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.75,0:18:33.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:34.75,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,65 centimeters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.82,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:47.56,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,So Manaka really does...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.55,Flashback,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.55,0:18:51.51,Flashback,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,if Manaka were to disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.86,0:18:54.32,Flashback,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,the one next to Hikari would be you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.02,0:18:58.16,Italics,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm awful... What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.08,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.08,0:19:06.29,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,They apparently used to keep carp there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:07.90,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:09.32,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,There was still garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:12.25,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little small for \Nfour people to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:13.98,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Four people"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:14.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.12,0:19:19.40,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'd be annoying always having\Nto consider the time while you work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.75,0:19:22.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei said it'd be fine to use as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:26.18,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're going to make \Na watering hole for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:27.47,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be a bother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.47,0:19:30.89,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Not at all, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.63,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.65,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,The girl with the really round eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:37.72,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Manaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.09,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I hope her fish is happy about it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.63,0:19:42.53,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Fish"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:49.96,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't... be so \Nkind to Manaka anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.50,0:19:52.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka has...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:54.69,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:01.09,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Curse me, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.62,0:20:05.36,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly why do you want to be cursed?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:07.69,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, w-well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.95,0:20:10.26,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,because it hurts to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:12.02,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.90,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Well um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.42,0:20:22.74,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You've always had\Nsomeone protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:26.17,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, Chisaki, and Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:30.75,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You should have just kept \Nstumbling along behind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:35.15,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,And now you're trying to go \Nsomewhere they can't protect you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:40.76,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You may need a small lie \Nor two to protect yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:42.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.39,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:46.83,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:47.86,Main,guy a,0000,0000,0000,,Just get over here, Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:51.37,Main,guy b,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna have to tell us \Neverything in front of Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:54.60,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me! I'll tell my dad myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.10,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:54.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Akari?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.60,0:20:56.56,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:00.78,Main,man a,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't concern you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.81,Main,man a,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay out of—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.81,0:21:05.07,Main,man b,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. It's about time they know too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:05.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.83,0:21:09.13,Main,man b,0000,0000,0000,,Just what happens when you\Nbreak the rules of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.35,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,"What happens"? What \Nare you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.35,0:21:13.71,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:15.06,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:16.58,Main,man a,0000,0000,0000,,So you've come, Chief Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.58,0:21:19.09,Main,man b,0000,0000,0000,,Akari is seeing a guy on the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.80,Main,man b,0000,0000,0000,,Someone saw them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:31.78,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to leave for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.78,0:21:33.18,Main,man a,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Priest...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:36.27,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I will talk to Akari myself.
